Class DatabaseDataObjectGenerator

java.lang.Object
  pizzaProgram.database.databaseUtils.DatabaseDataObjectGenerator

public class DatabaseDataObjectGenerator
extends Object

Class to generate dataObjects based on ResultSets sent to the methods of the class. All methods in the class are static.

Author:
